abstract: For nearly 200 years, historically black colleges and universities have educated thousands of students, but they continue to face an uncertain future.
snippet: For nearly 200 years, historically black colleges and universities have educated thousands of students, but they continue to face an uncertain future.
lead_paragraph: Since the 1930s, the women of Bennett College, one of the nation‚Äôs two historically black colleges for women, have dressed in white and sung their ‚ÄúPreference Song‚Äù over an annual breakfast. They wave white linen napkins in the air, cheering ‚Äúdear old Bennett College,‚Äù and welcome incoming freshmen.

abstract: Trump campaign aides and allies acknowledged that the California senator could be a vexing rival and that the Democratic race will be more unpredictable than they had thought.
snippet: Trump campaign aides and allies acknowledged that the California senator could be a vexing rival and that the Democratic race will be more unpredictable than they had thought.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON ‚Äî He would relish a run against Senator Elizabeth Warren and has dismissed Senator Bernie Sanders as ‚Äúcrazy.‚Äù He has worried about Joseph R. Biden Jr.‚Äôs standing in the polls, at the same time telling advisers that the former vice president is a male version of Hillary Clinton and that a matchup in 2020 is a race he knows how to run.
